ce/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SKATE CANADA:Broadcast Schedule  Liu, a two-time U.S. champion, skated her first Grand Prix program in three years.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997123864521894, \"rank\": 0.00027863347877460647, \"text\": \"U.S.\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She retired after winning bronze at the March 2022 World Championships.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier Friday, world champions Deanna Stellato-Dudek and Maxime Deschamps of Canada topped the pairs' short program with 73.23 points.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 864, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deanna_Stellato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Deanna Stellato-Dudek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deanna_Stellato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deanna_Stellato\"}, {\"begin\": 869, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxime_Deschamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maxime Deschamps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxime_Deschamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maxime_Deschamps\"}, {\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9974970690824208, \"rank\": 0.0022480609457634373, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentenc